# API / Route handler context

Editing API routes. See docs/CODING_STANDARDS.md §5, §11, §17

## Quick checks

- Validate input, return 400 for invalid
- Correct status codes (200, 400, 404, 500)
- No stack traces to client
- TypeScript types for payloads
